item.description: We will be having a Wapping Fair promotional booth at the town farmers market. This will be another chance to publicize the upcoming fair and all its attractions, including the varoius ways people can participate in the fair. The market is open from 10 - 2 p.m.. Volunteers are needed from 9:00 - 2:30. p.m.
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Jaycee members and booth
item.name: Promotional Booth at South Windsor Farmers Market
